{"tid":2279133,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中大新亞書院「NA Can」入不敷支本月底結業　知名紅豆冰或成絕唱","createTime":"2020-11-09T14:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T03:27:20.000Z","uid":225931,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"3c35a67a5c2fb78d2d5280fe5db57a2431ca1e16","tid":2279133,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T14:33:48.000Z","msg":"Facebook專頁「CUHK Secrets」今日刊登投稿指，新亞書院學生餐廳「NA Can」將於本月結業，投稿者不捨餐廳經理、收銀及水吧職員，慨嘆下一個餐廳承辦商或不再能製作出相同質素的紅豆冰，「想試就多啲幫襯，叫佢地整埋依個月啦。」<br />\n<br />\n「NA Can」最為中大學生及校友熟知的食品，包括紅豆冰、芝士火腿卷、炒蛋及雙餸飯等，不少在校中大生及校友均留言稱感惋惜，有人留言指：「防疫好成功，但NA can死咗。」<br />\n<br />\n中大回覆查詢時證實，新亞餐廳將經營至11月底，結業的主要原因為過去一年受疫情影響下，於校內用膳的學生及教職員人流減少，令其生意受到影響。校方指，為減輕餐廳的經營成本，新亞書院曾作出各項特別安排，包括減免部份管理費，惟在長期入不敷支情況下，經營者最終決定結業。<br />\n<br />\n新亞書院尊重經營者的決定，稍後將展開招標程序，務求盡快物色合適的服務承辦商接手經營餐廳。"},{"pid":"e21c30fcb235358c72b302cf68d02b43554d0b32","tid":2279133,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T14:34:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8911804ce4e6d33ee548fe72455c8086de76f3ac","tid":2279133,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T14:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4419b5ad91a879b1ddfecefe74cf306bf9febab","tid":2279133,"uid":178078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T14:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌，得返CC Can"},{"pid":"438b42c7011a38ebf8c4b4cd790d9ec800125e97","tid":2279133,"uid":302414,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"p